{"tid":538264,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"地球自轉一圈24小時","createTime":"2018-01-23T13:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T11:12:14.000Z","uid":9345,"like":3,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"b67097c4e22d6781bff54de18ded1a7f5058d1f3","tid":538264,"uid":9345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n如果搭飛機搭長途d地點<br />\n假如去A,B兩個地方  兩個地方距離起點，即係x個點係一樣 如圖<br />\n咁飛機速度一樣 飛既距離一樣<br />\n但因為地球跟住個軸自轉 會唔會因為自轉問題飛去a點會快過b點到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/210101_19bc306e0d1bbec331915d304dce266c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F210101_19bc306e0d1bbec331915d304dce266c.jpg&h=4f9e9ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無知一問，可能你地覺得係弱智問題，但想求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac1e5666a977009335f5767aac79affbe4fe5b6","tid":538264,"uid":9345,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"推一個"},{"pid":"6cc1ed30d42004679e119e97663dbe457dbf52a0","tid":538264,"uid":89146,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:07:29.000Z","msg":"會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飛機去程同回程個時間都有啲唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bef08afd160250ee4b26cda10378288bdaf365c","tid":538264,"uid":9345,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飛機去程同回程個時間都有啲唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟最遠都只係去過時差1個鐘既地方 有時加減番就唔多覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e3e8072a95909f052d9cb9e594cf1628a3a167","tid":538264,"uid":135132,"like":9,"dislike":32,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:44:50.000Z","ms